{"type":null,"faqId":38952,"title":"拿到手环后，如何开始使用？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\r\n.p1{text-indent:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.p2{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.p3{margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.p4{margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.p5{text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.11111111in;}\r\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<p></p>\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">拿到手环后，请按以下步骤操作，以便正常使用手环。</span></p>\n<p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">1.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 7pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN-CONVERTED-SPACE>&nbsp;</SPAN-CONVERTED-SPACE></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">在华为应用市场或</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">App Store</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">中搜索并下载“华为穿戴”</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">APP</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">2.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 7pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN-CONVERTED-SPACE>&nbsp;</SPAN-CONVERTED-SPACE></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">连接充电器手环自动开机，进入配对状态。</span></p>\n<p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box; TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><span><a href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7425f_jjxtu.png\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: #666666; TEXT-DECORATION: none; text-underline: none\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7425f_jjxtu.png\" width=\"481\" height=\"353\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151016145421948001.jpg\"></span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">说明：您也可以按手环背面孔键开</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">/</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">关机。建议您使用手机卡槽顶针或者圆珠笔按压孔键，不要使用钢针等过于尖锐的物体，以防损坏孔键。</span></p>\n<p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">3.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 7pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN-CONVERTED-SPACE>&nbsp;</SPAN-CONVERTED-SPACE></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">打开手机蓝牙，通过</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">APP</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">搜索手环，点击</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">honor zero-xxx</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">4.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 7pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN-CONVERTED-SPACE>&nbsp;</SPAN-CONVERTED-SPACE></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">点击手环屏幕上的</span><span -converted-space=\"\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">&nbsp;</span></span><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">√</span></b><SPAN-CONVERTED-SPACE><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'; COLOR: black\">完成连接。</span></SPAN-CONVERTED-SPACE></p>\n<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><a href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/74260_0trv4.png\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; COLOR: #666666; TEXT-DECORATION: none; text-underline: none\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/74260_0trv4.png\" width=\"606\" height=\"517\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151016145421534002.jpg\"></span></a></span>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4262","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441